  "briefing": "Hard-A (phased): 50 blocks across 5 districts, revealed in 3 phases. Phase 1 \u2014 I1+I2 (B1-B20): west sectors with tight infra (I2 power=82). B9, B10, B15, B20 are green corridors \u2014 they form a greenway belt that severs direct service paths. Phase 2 \u2014 I3 (B21-B30) revealed: B25 protected, B26 entertainment zone. I3 needs transit. Phase 3 \u2014 I4+I5 (B31-B50) revealed: B36 entertainment zone, B47 protected, I4 sewer=28. All constraints are baked in from the start \u2014 plan around them, not past them. Service coverage is measured by graph hops; district equity enforced per zone.",
